{
  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"c9b3ceb9c65cecd0e430461780784f14\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"494c3440d1283c945e999ff1a9c0e3e5\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"03bf44f005196ba5608fdee4cf08040e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">语雀提供了一个简约但足够强大的在线文档编辑器，在提供基础文本操作的同时，可以在文档中插入脑图、在线视频、表格、公式等丰富功能。</span></p><p id=\"027b4294cd6fab0f253fc907128ef7eb\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h2 id=\"QAELu\"><span class=\"ne-text\">编辑器结构介绍</span></h2><p id=\"ee0552c172fb8cdda9540d2927ae1931\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"0b564f66c16c36364f48f88ccbb2255d\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">编辑器的顶部是菜单栏、中间是工具栏、尾部是正文输入。通过菜单栏对文档的一些属性进行操作，比如文档设置。通过工具栏可以让你快速在正文输入的时候插入对应的格式。</span></p><p id=\"db6fbb328cbb5cf78a41aab13e90d022\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"39465b97876b5741ac4dd06b9cbd6c23\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1636524932390-094c86f5-24a9-4e92-9719-b70fe4bf904b.png\" width=\"898.6666666666666\" id=\"u88ecc557\" class=\"ne-image\"><span class=\"ne-text\">                                    </span></p><h2 id=\"98862a0f\"><span class=\"ne-text\">菜单栏</span></h2><p id=\"2b464767d4a18f4801a146c31979503b\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">菜单栏主要分两个部分，左侧是新建和跳转入口，点击左侧图标唤起新建入口。同时你可以点击知识库标题返回到知识库。</span></p><p id=\"32d7b1905abff716ecfda4bedd428263\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"d2d1702ae51928351dd665c8cd20d2ce\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1634094077087-cf84a351-0339-4a79-ad6e-4cecfb4e7d60.png\" width=\"296\" id=\"u92e4da79\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"30c241f4a8404e141b63306db6550936\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"5696087b754515afb9aa6569b140503a\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"a69deeba9b42fca3ad8df5288ce036fa\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">右侧是关于这个文档相关的操作，比如设置页面宽度、排版风格、查看历史、修改文档信息，邀请别人参与编辑等。</span></p><p id=\"eb43798efc6e3b9b0c4a5b6b7e525a5a\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"9ba104e99165b6f2d17ddbdbe1bca578\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1634094204842-2d1b30fc-77b8-4a26-87f1-acef46d8dd0c.png\" width=\"216.66666666666666\" id=\"u80958594\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"e63de058929221ec1f579f60abdd032d\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h3 id=\"f56ae67a\"><span class=\"ne-text\">统计信息</span></h3><p id=\"d81a7ec3b3f7121c4047f0e7d4e60b14\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"79bfd2eab0a8f3331db9af4b6a3a977c\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">点击</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">文档右上角「...」</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">,可在面板下方直观看到统计信息。<br /></span><span class=\"ne-text\">统计信息可以看到当前文档中有多少字数，创建时间、创建者、最后编辑者以及该文档所有的贡献者。</span></p><p id=\"u23f5247e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><p id=\"u5e698dd7\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1634094521145-4da43501-bfc1-44ca-bb93-f52572eac619.png\" width=\"167.33333333333334\" id=\"u22f91982\" class=\"ne-image\"><span class=\"ne-text\">                                    </span></p><p id=\"810ec3eb865eb8c315a06a6821c415da\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"> </span></p><h3 id=\"62f79c83\"><span class=\"ne-text\">文档设置</span></h3><p id=\"3fda368742d2adffdce74b375f7c2182\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"797a34fa22b1c478f132fe9d9444443a\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">文档设置可以对文档的标题和路径进行调整，还有呼声最高的功能，公开知识库单独对一篇文档进行加密。加密后在文档标题上会显示一把小锁。</span></p><p id=\"3eb4409e79cbab0cf6ae65e5ddc674f1\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"156b4a75da97c27053b71b48b4a17885\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/84147/1581686063452-560d5029-21b5-440c-a29d-7947c813193c.png\" width=\"610.9971313476562\" id=\"zPrnU\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"13364eb55ce30cfa6bc89f4af83a1c24\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"f6be83605a1b1aa40f6f403919582644\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">                                   </span></p><h3 id=\"a1c90d39\"><span class=\"ne-text\">历史版本</span></h3><p id=\"ec513ac887eee3610680c3a61209f8a4\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"0724ac85cf648854858ca1000326d675\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">点击菜单里的历史版本，或者发布按钮旁边的历史，你可以进入历史界面。找到这篇文档所有的历史，并可以进行选择版本恢复。</span></p><p id=\"9e6e1d17dbb5f1b3556c01f62b0ba28e\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"86aff5eb293c4d9bd3bf6d9673835034\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"c749ef8d5cc6e0a42fdee2c30e733a94\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1634094684893-6d3ffa00-c500-4188-b3b6-1a70b22a3113.png\" width=\"936\" id=\"u2a3789d4\" class=\"ne-image\"><span class=\"ne-text\">                                   </span></p><h2 id=\"c4115df3\"><span class=\"ne-text\">工具条</span></h2><p id=\"29bdaf1e60ea690788357f634e1e1b91\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"19cf4f8ce62376237c5b68ec1d671af7\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在工具条上除了常规的快捷操作，我们引入了新的功能“卡片”，下面是对卡片的介绍：</span></p><p id=\"d2cab7786211409c711f1dbe8b2c5e4c\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><div class=\"ne-quote\"><p id=\"ac267bdcd6fe307c69263279bc56fa96\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #8C8C8C\">卡片是语雀文档里的一个特殊组成部分，它可以是某个功能，也可以是一个独立编辑器，或者又是一个小组件。第三方开发者可以接入卡片，我们为其开放独立编辑权限，它可以联动</span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #8C8C8C; background-color: #FADB14\">工具条</span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #8C8C8C\">和</span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #8C8C8C; background-color: #FADB14\">设置</span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #8C8C8C\">，甚至进入一个独立的编辑界面。卡片给文档编辑者提供更多专业的功能，赋予更多可能性。</span></p></div><p id=\"c390fe0937a42055dfb26874bcb9f6d5\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"a3ceeed9aff0e95ab50b355085474141\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1636525262290-dca7836d-bea1-4ab5-94bb-635d68fdf528.png\" width=\"385.9886169433594\" id=\"u36d52815\" class=\"ne-image\"><span class=\"ne-text\">                                    </span></p><p id=\"0b0aefa5de2aefd8a737b277e632533a\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"73c56f615e150edd1a15b4caeba66a4f\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"7b34955121cf4e998ceffb2e251ab9f0\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">点击工具条左侧的插入</span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #262626\">卡片 Icon，选择你需要的卡片，比如 表格、图片、附件、脑图。同时你也可以直接在文档段落首行输入 “/” 或者行内使用 “command+/”，也可以快速唤起卡片控件。在 “/” 后输入相对应的卡片名字可以直接激活对应的卡片。如果没有匹配到卡片会被当成文字处理。</span></p><p id=\"58ef24f7f21861b753131d93bc5b7b7f\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"078e6b2ceeeb2e238b8edd5ae1015fbc\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1636525293017-5ee595e7-4d04-4eac-bef0-6fd9396c41f3.png\" width=\"846\" id=\"asUfY\" class=\"ne-image\"><span class=\"ne-text\">                                    </span></p><p id=\"ua7b69e5f\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">另外，在特色卡片面板中增加最近使用功能，最多展示四个最近使用的应用。</span></p><p id=\"u05eca1a2\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1634095146498-34eff12a-3435-41c9-95cb-4fbc11d949a4.png\" width=\"173.33333333333334\" id=\"ufdbace67\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u1ef27b49\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><p id=\"080f8da1f6d65ec1d44434d4f726d578\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">目前支持的卡片类型如下：</span></p><p id=\"f5abc304324c9dfcaf0966ca4f64cf40\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"f49feb13e0130bb4ed0629db68af4c26\"><span class=\"ne-text\">图片</span></li><li id=\"acc05e18a34851f03bc6bff38391d33f\"><span class=\"ne-text\">表格</span></li><li id=\"c49c6f8ec968b1dfdb4e3e8dc994d39f\"><span class=\"ne-text\">附件</span></li><li id=\"991609e8dac6534d39e5008cbef67d1f\"><span class=\"ne-text\">公式</span></li><li id=\"d4ab78318b9d9c218ee5bfd0b4287b6a\"><span class=\"ne-text\">代码块</span></li><li id=\"59384728ed8e1db0a8eaa151f22817e3\"><span class=\"ne-text\">脑图</span></li><li id=\"71390301285bfccfbdd65ad73a493feb\"><span class=\"ne-text\">流程图</span></li><li id=\"3f13ac0855e9bce3fb0cf058406ece82\"><span class=\"ne-text\">文本绘图（PlantUML 等）</span></li><li id=\"c1a61851aa6cc3d66fefa43be099fc98\"><span class=\"ne-text\">加密文本</span></li><li id=\"0e61ab68300c8b6aedeaa2dad0a0cd2e\"><span class=\"ne-text\">语雀文档</span></li><li id=\"9edd63827179b9ba6116a69497d43c96\"><span class=\"ne-text\">本地文档（Word、PDF、Keynote 等）</span></li><li id=\"faaf3109b634f837a003983cf62e9fdd\"><span class=\"ne-text\">本地视频</span></li><li id=\"a625ba836540aaaf832d65eb9072cf4a\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在线视频（哔哩哔哩、优酷）</span></li><li id=\"181e53133de86111b39078bb7fcc74be\"><span class=\"ne-text\">第三方服务</span></li></ul><p id=\"90d317bc2f7ad15a8ee8f72f66adca13\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"1cca4ca7d14bc0f5a3dac75eacb96ccc\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">整个卡片它拥有几个部分，正文编辑器区域+独立编辑器区域+正文顶部工具条+卡片工具条+右侧设置，后续会将能力开放给第三方开放者。下面是表格作为卡片的一个基础展示：</span></p><p id=\"4eb0f2791484baf6474c7612085d32ce\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"fffb24dfc48111528cac991b285c3fb7\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1636525325211-86eddd3e-5a1a-43c5-8265-e5fc07f8516e.png\" width=\"1355\" id=\"u4318d809\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"5fc883791abab7628a5af7f03caeb3c8\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">                                   </span></p><p id=\"9ffae686463a3b5809c0fcb785ce86ac\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">当你操作表格的时候，顶部的工具条会切换成适合表格的工具条，你可以在上面进行输入操作，比如对文本的处理，比如对单元格的处理。卡片左上角还有卡片本身的工具条，可以进行复制和删除处理。</span></p><p id=\"uca60ea38\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><p id=\"50ef5f334435b39c75af238a211e82f9\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1636525342861-d74594fe-800e-44b0-a262-e13b3a8b8658.png\" width=\"1200\" id=\"ub2393be3\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u643258fa\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><p id=\"udb5b953a\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">当你将鼠标悬浮在表格卡片的上方，会快速唤起操作面板，你可以设置表格的</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">「全宽展示」</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">，也可以点击</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">「全屏」</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">进入卡片的独立操作界面。<br /><br /></span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1636525376003-5c97e047-1ac9-4fa8-af25-627fdaf484a9.png\" width=\"1343\" id=\"u286e3164\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u6d11b13a\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"fc614b32c22b57adf94c0d5193f2b5a9\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">当你进入卡片的独立编辑界面的时候，整个正文输入会变成纯卡片操作。</span></p><p id=\"e0edfd074c33df079b5577f95fa27075\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"555346fe59edb5d6086f96cf4dfddc2b\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1636525426018-8d8d85a0-3256-483f-a932-bfe850cee3ea.png\" width=\"1361\" id=\"u65da210b\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><h2 id=\"aHeNa\"><span class=\"ne-text\">大纲</span></h2><p id=\"u3718712d\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u792fcdab\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">大纲在最右侧中间位置，你可以选择隐藏大纲，点击隐藏大纲后，大纲会缩起，变成mini状态；或者钉住大纲，固定在正文右侧显示</span></p><p id=\"uc7923efa\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><p id=\"u0ac7fe00\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">隐藏大纲效果：</span></p><p id=\"ude6d8fa4\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1636525482637-72816157-4aa0-46da-b01c-8fcbe908c167.png\" width=\"1352\" id=\"u6855ed83\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"uf99032ec\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">钉住大纲效果：</span></p><p id=\"u39a2d6f0\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1636525490518-572dc661-8210-403c-bff4-125f419b5d52.png\" width=\"1419\" id=\"u6627d374\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"ud6ddfcf5\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h2 id=\"b7f53bbd\"><span class=\"ne-text\">正文区域</span></h2><p id=\"146a3240c0e44c941ee6bd88416d821a\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"e86de21064265e5852265a39dd3e4b52\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">正文区域功能是对内容的输入，可以在这里编辑你的文档。同时你可以点击右上角</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">「...」按钮</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">，选择排版风格，或者超宽模式。</span></p><p id=\"60b63f0b71ea314630049e720553b12d\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u9da0dcab\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1636525609732-3320794f-06b8-4efa-a614-47eb447f128a.png\" width=\"1427\" id=\"uea124861\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"c823e53a8b13777a66dc193c97468907\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"fe20f07a928ed7d5a8ed051c5e44a010\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">开启超宽模式后，页面宽度变为超宽显示，整个输入面积会变大，在这样的面积下你可以尽情的利用好页面的空间。同时文档发布后，阅读页面会跟着变动，变成超宽显示。</span></p><p id=\"u6849a53c\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u00c5a1f7\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1634095743367-884d5ced-7e1d-4556-bb36-64a2801e10af.png\" width=\"933.3333333333334\" id=\"sgK0e\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u62ef568a\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u9d37165e\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"bea614d277bb700cc79841464c3c8a54\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"521275fcd3e2417b098d55ed614524d8\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(23, 26, 29)\">如果对语雀有任何的建议或意见，可以提交反馈：</span><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/feedbacks/new\" data-href=\"https://www.yuque.com/feedbacks/new\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">语雀反馈通道 </span></a><span class=\"ne-text\">  感谢你的支持！</span></p><p id=\"u9396829a\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><p id=\"ub894a418\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p></div>",
  "slug": 32765702,
  "title": "在线文档编辑器"
}